---
//import image from '../../public/img/nav.png';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Shop</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Our webshop supports both people and the environment. Let's create a positive impact on our environment and society."
    />
  </head>

  <nav class="image">
    <img
      src="../../public/img/nav.png"
      alt="navbar picture"
      width="100%"
      height="auto"
    />
  </nav>

  <main data-speed="0.5">
    <div class="gif-container">
      <video
        data-speed="0.5"
        src="../../public/animation/walk.mp4"
        width="100%"
        height="auto"
        autoplay
        loop
      >
      </video>
    </div>

    <div class="pink-box">
      <h2>
        Når du handler i vores webshop, støtter du både mennesker og miljøet.
        Lad os sammen skabe en positiv indvirkning på både vores miljø og
        samfund.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="video-container">
      <iframe
        width="100%"
        height="600"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vunPLrUupF4"
        title="YouTube video player"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="pink-banner">
      <h3>
        Vi er taknemmelige for vores talentfulde team, der gør det muligt for os
        at skabe smukke, bæredygtige produkter og samtidig have en positiv
        indflydelse på samfundet.
      </h3>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2022 Your Webshop. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

  <style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: "nunito";

      src: url(../../public/font/nunito-extrabold-webfont.woff);
    }
    main {
      perspective: 1px;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow-y: scroll;
      /* font-family: "nunito"; */
    }
    h2,
    h3,
    p {
      font-family: "nunito" "sans-serif";
    }

    main > * {
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }

    main > [data-speed] {
      position: relative;
      transform-origin: 50% 0;
      transform: translate3d(0, calc(var(--scroll-y) * var(--speed)), 0);
      transition: transform 0.5s ease-out;
    }

    .gif-container {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0;
      /* padding: 2rem 0; */
    }

    .pink-box {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 4rem;
      background-color: #f1e0dd;
      text-align: center;
      font-family:;
    }

    .video-container {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      /* padding: 2rem 0; */
    }

    .pink-banner {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem;
      background-color: #f1e0dd;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* .video-container > video[data-speed] {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.5);
    } */
  </style>


</html>
